{"tid":1747401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"贏民調，輸選舉？選舉唔係淨係鬥民意","createTime":"2019-11-23T07:54:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T08:21:53.000Z","uid":72875,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d50de206c9f64c4bef52784361d6b7a500bd5d0d","tid":1747401,"uid":72875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">更重要係鬥出席率</span></strong><br />\n2016年特朗普都係靠高出席率爆冷取勝<br />\n<br />\n香港合資格選民得300萬人<br />\n你地只要當聽日區選係有不反對通知的和理非遊行<br />\n去票站行個圈投票<br />\n咁就已經贏硬<br />\n<br />\n但係而家你地做緊咩？<br />\n內鬥辯論唔好投對家/白票？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你地只要浪費時間心力去內鬥<br />\n分化撚就已經贏左<br />\n<br />\n唔該停止再辯論<br />\n即刻對外文宣叫人出黎投票<br />\n要好似叫人出黎遊行咁落力！</span><br />\n<br />\n投邊個？<br />\n<a href=\"https://vote4.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvote4.hk&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpEwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=7ae6990b\" target=\"_blank\">https://vote4.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHFscSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHFscSY.jpg&h=8e4c6bce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77088e21fe1a6d982076d482b12912160780fb47","tid":1747401,"uid":72875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:00:16.000Z","msg":"連登仔<br />\n我屌曬你地老母<br />\n一開熱門<br />\n一堆陳雲白票post<br />\n拉鳩佢落去啦<br />\n根本唔撚使討論"},{"pid":"2dd3cc036844009a31ac08eed2d688461159fec9","tid":1747401,"uid":282836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:02:44.000Z","msg":"【11-24 告急】 投本土泛民，不投建制，連登每小時245留言討論投對家，有圖<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezKewS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezKewS</a>"},{"pid":"51ef20ed16916d981f6f2e3d6001c7d3cbdac848","tid":1747401,"uid":72875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:03:16.000Z","msg":"跟本聽日要吹大雞<br />\n和理非咁耐無機會去真不反對遊行<br />\n聽日係大好機會<br />\n動員到200萬遊行咁多人<br />\n你區選贏撚硬"},{"pid":"7e80e328a19fcefd374abeacb4ffecebd3c8635b","tid":1747401,"uid":72875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:05:48.000Z","msg":"屌曬你地老母"},{"pid":"e7224d543363ef42396e3d58a8dffb63ee39a055","tid":1747401,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:07:10.000Z","msg":"**** 眾籌 ****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(由於中大民調欠缺資金做今次反送中民調，我們的眾籌會同時加入新項目，籌到的款項亦會用作資助中大民調)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先75%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n第六期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpEwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=b1e15c36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fn&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpEwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=d0092063\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\